title: Pressure? Harvick long ago proved he could handle it
text: Pressure? Harvick long ago proved he could handle it Monday, 5 October 2015 (5 minutes ago) Pressure? Kevin Harvick says needing to win Sunday's AAA 400 to advance to the next round of the 2015 Chase for the Sprint Cup was a walk in the park compared to what he went through early in his career.
